---
name    : detroit-vclog
version : 0.1.0
title   : Detroit VCLog
summary : VCLog plugin for Detroit

description:
  VCLog plugin for Detroit build system. This plugin
  generates changelog and/or history documents for a
  project during the document phase.

resources:
  home: http://detroit.github.com/
  code: http://github.com/detroit/detroit-vclog
  mail: http://groups.google.com/group/rubyworks-mailinglist

